WWW::RaptureReady version 0.1
=============================

This module provides an interface to the Rapture Ready [0] Rapture
Index [1].  The rapture index is the "prophetic speedometer of
end-time activity".

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP::UserAgent

